      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To mandate minimum periods of rest and recuperation for units and members of the regular and reserve components of the Armed Forces between deployments for Operation Iraqi Freedom or Operation Enduring Freedom.</title>
